# Claude Code Project Rules for Gangs Online

## Dashboard Architecture

### CRITICAL: Metronic Template
- **DO NOT MODIFY** `/packages/dashboard/metronic/` directory
- This is a REFERENCE TEMPLATE ONLY for UI patterns and components
- All actual development work should be done in `/packages/dashboard/main/`
- If you accidentally modify metronic, immediately revert the changes
- Metronic is preserved as a clean reference for future UI development

### Active Dashboard
- **Main Dashboard**: `/packages/dashboard/main/` - This is the ONLY dashboard to modify
- All new features, pages, and components should be added to `main` dashboard
- Follow the existing patterns in `main` for consistency

## Git Workflow

### Branch Naming
- Feature branches should follow: `claude/feature-name-{sessionId}`
- Always push to the branch specified in the task description
- Use descriptive commit messages in Traditional Chinese

### Commit Standards
- Write commit messages in English with clear descriptions
- Include lists of changes in the commit body
- Always mention affected modules/components

## Development Guidelines

### Code Style
- Use TypeScript for all new code
- Follow existing naming conventions in the codebase
- Prefer functional components over class components (React)
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling (as seen in main dashboard)

### File Organization
- Keep feature-related files grouped together
- Follow Next.js App Router conventions for page structure
- Use barrel exports (index.ts) for cleaner imports

### Testing
- Always test changes in the main dashboard
- Ensure dark mode compatibility for all UI changes
- Check mobile responsiveness

## Communication
- Respond in Traditional Chinese (繁體中文)
- Be concise but thorough in explanations
- Ask for clarification when requirements are unclear

## Phase 16-2 Specific Rules
- NPC management features are in `/packages/dashboard/main/src/app/npc/`
- Prisma schema is in `/packages/dashboard/metronic/prisma/` (for reference)
- All NPC-related API integration should be prepared but noted as "需要後端 API 整合"
